CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS AND ADMINISTRATIVE ACTIONS

May 1, 2003

MOTIONS AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

1991-2137. State v. Campbell.

Hamilton App. No. C-890330. Upon consideration of appellant’s motion to suspend S.Ct.Prac.R. XIV(4)(B),

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion be, and hereby is, granted.
